 Turney Duff, author of 'The Buy 
Side: A Wall Street Trader's Tale of Spectacular Excess' says 
his journey mirrored that of the market. Duff says he collapsed 
at the same time as the tech bubble burst. Duff talks with 
Bloomberg's Vonnie Quinn on Bloomberg Radio's "The Hays 
Advantage."    (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 16:08
 